>
	<p>
	<h2 class="text-[#4BC8EC]">Managerial Economics by Matthew Metzgar, PhD</h2>

  <p class="mb-4">
    Learn managerial economics with current real‐world content that connects with today’s students. This textbook starts with the value creation philosophy of Peter Drucker and ends with the long‐term challenge of business sustainability. Along the way, students will learn how to successfully apply economics to managerial decisions across a variety of situations.
  </p>

  <!-- Inline‐style: force the browser to render the cover at 75 px wide -->
